MobilePurchaseOrderReceiptCommentForm is a Form
    propagate as a drill
    title is "ReceiptComment"
    restrict action MobileCreate
    restrict action Create
    Actions
        action is save
            label is "_"
            hide when invalid
        action is save and new
            hide when invalid
            valid when (false)
    Layout
        single column
            CommentTitle
                label is "Title"
            CommentType
                label is "Type"
            CommentText
                label is "Comment"
                use text area of 8 lines
            Attachment.File
                label is "Attachment"
